- run tmp-replication script
  sleep 7h; while sleep 5m; do sudo -u hdfs hdfs dfs -setrep 1 /tmp/*.zip; done
- suspend map builds
  for WID in 0119156-210914110416597-oozie-oozi-C; do oozie job -oozie http://c5oozie.gbif.org:11000/oozie/ -suspend $WID; done
- update srcpath
- mkdir on HDFS (done)
- aim for 4 processes running on each server
- C5 should take 10 files per process per server
- C6 should take 12 files per process per server
- C7 should take 18 files per process per server

Each file takes about 15 minutes to process.

Then run monthly-cloud-upload
